00:23:02.745 --> 00:23:05.115
If Lee Woo Gyeom can truly cure
an incurable disease,

00:23:05.945 --> 00:23:09.445
I believe that's ample reason
to consider it in his sentencing.

00:23:10.015 --> 00:23:13.185
No.
The court's deliberation on this is over.

00:23:19.725 --> 00:23:23.095
Filing a constitutional petition
is at the discretion of the defense,

00:23:23.735 --> 00:23:24.835
You may proceed if you must,

00:23:25.895 --> 00:23:28.835
but the appeal will proceed as scheduled.
Understood?

00:23:29.635 --> 00:23:30.635
Yes, Your Honor.

00:23:33.205 --> 00:23:34.245
(Attorney Park, the article is a hit!)

00:23:34.305 --> 00:23:35.705
Do you have anything further?

00:23:36.145 --> 00:23:38.175
- Nothing further.
- Then we are adjourned.

00:23:38.245 --> 00:23:39.245
Your Honor.

00:23:42.645 --> 00:23:44.355
Would you please
take a look at this article?

00:23:46.185 --> 00:23:49.255
("Serial Killer Lee Woo Gyeom
Saves a Life in Prison!")

00:23:55.265 --> 00:23:56.265
One moment.

00:23:57.065 --> 00:23:58.735
(Director Oh Hyeon Deuk)

00:24:00.205 --> 00:24:01.665
Yes, Mr. Chief Justice.

00:24:03.165 --> 00:24:05.005
Yes. I've just seen the article myself,

00:24:06.175 --> 00:24:08.175
("Serial Killer Lee Woo Gyeom
Saves a Life in Prison!")

00:24:09.175 --> 00:24:11.945
I'll find out what the situation is.

00:24:18.215 --> 00:24:20.255
He was cured by a blood transfusion
from Lee Woo Gyeom?

00:24:20.685 --> 00:24:23.855
Yes. I just found out
from the article myself,

00:24:24.325 --> 00:24:25.995
so I'm looking into the details now.

00:24:26.055 --> 00:24:28.565
Seriously, what's with
that jerk Lee Woo Gyeom?

00:24:29.065 --> 00:24:31.235
If he had something to prove,
he should've done it way sooner.

00:24:31.635 --> 00:24:34.505
He had to know that a death penalty case
goes to a third trial.

00:24:35.165 --> 00:24:36.165
Goodness!

00:24:36.805 --> 00:24:38.575
What are you going to do now?

00:24:39.435 --> 00:24:42.105
Director Oh.
Let's not get ahead of ourselves.

00:24:42.345 --> 00:24:43.545
The trial isn't over yet.

00:24:44.115 --> 00:24:45.915
- In a situation like this...
- My reputation is on the line,

00:24:45.915 --> 00:24:47.485
and I chose to take this case.

00:24:48.215 --> 00:24:52.585
- Please, don't doubt me.
- What? Hey, do you even hear yourself?

00:24:56.055 --> 00:24:57.095
This court,

00:24:57.355 --> 00:24:59.695
after carefully reviewing
the defendant Lee Woo Gyeom's...

00:25:00.095 --> 00:25:03.865
recent act of providing
medical treatment in prison,

00:25:04.295 --> 00:25:08.665
has determined that it is necessary
to verify his medical abilities.

00:25:08.865 --> 00:25:12.275
An unprecedented decision has been made
in South Korea's constitutional history.

00:25:12.575 --> 00:25:16.945
The court handling the Lee Woo Gyeom case
has approved the medical demonstration.

