How did this happen?

00:25:21.885 --> 00:25:24.115
Someone named Professor Han Sang Ho
came to the hospital...

00:25:24.385 --> 00:25:25.385
Professor Han Sang Ho?

00:25:25.755 --> 00:25:29.325
According to the attending physician,
Lee Woo Gyeom called Prof. Han Sang Ho,

00:25:29.385 --> 00:25:31.855
and he confirmed that Bae Geun Hyeok
was transfused with Lee Woo Gyeom's blood.

00:25:32.125 --> 00:25:33.995
What about the files I requested
from Detective Gong?

00:25:34.125 --> 00:25:35.125
I left them over there.

00:25:35.525 --> 00:25:38.195
I checked Lee Woo Gyeom's visitor log
and the surrounding CCTV footage...

00:25:38.265 --> 00:25:39.835
and filtered out anyone
who seemed suspicious.

00:25:46.735 --> 00:25:48.805
(Han Sang Ho, Medical Professional)

00:25:48.875 --> 00:25:51.675
(Han Sang Ho, Medical Professional)

00:25:59.155 --> 00:26:00.285
(Jinnam Medical Research Institute)

00:26:08.665 --> 00:26:10.295
(Chief Pyo Kang Won)

00:26:25.515 --> 00:26:26.815
Hello, Prosecutor Cha.

00:26:28.315 --> 00:26:29.315
Prosecutor.

00:26:29.845 --> 00:26:30.985
How have you been?

00:26:33.625 --> 00:26:34.625
The thing is...

00:26:35.355 --> 00:26:37.225
I came across some information,

00:26:37.755 --> 00:26:39.555
and I was about to leak it to the press,

00:26:40.495 --> 00:26:42.725
but I was afraid of
the earful you'd give me.

00:26:44.265 --> 00:26:45.735
I'm a little busy.

00:26:46.395 --> 00:26:47.765
Just get to the point.

00:26:49.035 --> 00:26:50.035
You really...

00:26:51.175 --> 00:26:52.435
never change, do you?

00:26:53.805 --> 00:26:55.775
What is it you have for me?

00:26:58.645 --> 00:27:00.075
Attorney Park's daughter...

00:27:01.285 --> 00:27:02.745
is terminally ill.

00:27:05.185 --> 00:27:08.385
His wife is a doctor,
so instead of taking her elsewhere,

00:27:09.225 --> 00:27:13.055
she's apparently treating their daughter
at the hospital where she works.

00:27:13.925 --> 00:27:16.325
I'd bet that's why he took
Lee Woo Gyeom's case, don't you think?

00:27:19.795 --> 00:27:23.035
I'm not really interested
in people's family drama.

00:27:23.875 --> 00:27:26.935
How about another fun fact, then?

00:27:27.345 --> 00:27:29.345
(The Prosecution)

00:27:32.275 --> 00:27:33.685
