(Park Han Jun, Hong Jae Hee)

00:27:40.525 --> 00:27:41.655
So you didn't know.

00:27:44.655 --> 00:27:47.725
Then I take it you know Professor Han.

00:27:48.765 --> 00:27:50.025
Professor Han?

