00:38:25.395 --> 00:38:26.665
Jae Hee, I'm so sorry.

00:38:27.765 --> 00:38:29.105
It's all my fault.

00:38:29.905 --> 00:38:30.905
I see.

00:38:31.405 --> 00:38:35.205
- There are so many.
- A ton! Let's go check it out.

00:38:35.275 --> 00:38:36.405
- Ji Yeon.
- Let's go.

00:38:36.475 --> 00:38:37.545
Mom.

00:38:38.515 --> 00:38:39.945
- Say goodbye.
- Bye!

00:38:40.015 --> 00:38:41.785
- Bye.
- Bye.

00:38:42.315 --> 00:38:44.185
- My favorite!
- Hold my hand, sweetie.

